do you know who is watching you alarming yesterday i had a drs appt and my year old daughter had to drive me there i signed in and in no time saw the dr when i went to check out in the lobby a man who was years old noticed my daughter he smiled at her and she smiled back thinking nothing of it the alarm came this morning when she got on her computer and saw that he went to her myspace and found her he wrote her a message not even knowing her name or address i contacted the drs office who then notified the officials she currently has a private site but this is very alarming when someone can find you and at what lengths someone will go to get what they want his message was quite disturbing please please make certain to have your kids alert you if they have this happen to them and always be cautious as to who may be looking over your shoulder what would you have done my daughter was with me the whole time even in the exam room she never said a word to anyone she will soon be they cover the name of the patient after they have signed in so i have no idea how he could have found her none at all hello thank you for letting us know about this creep it really freaks me out how complete strangers can find anything out about you by just using your name my doctor's office has a very tight security system where they call numbers instead of names and then we go into a private room and update them on any new current personal information this way no weirdos or creeps can overhear us and they don't know what our names are my daughter is supervised very closely by me or my husband when she is online and we only allow her to go to websites that we approve of and we are watching her like a hawk the whole time it is really scary that it is so quick and easy to find out personal information about anyone it just sends chills up and down my spine shudders thank you for making us aware of how vulnerable all of our personal information really is and how important it is to be careful of how m